.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm daddbmk
.Nd add a bookmark in 
.Pa $HOME/.bookmarks
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
display selected link in 
.Xr dmenu 1
get the page title with 
.Xr curl 1
then open in the default text editor for further modifications.

Each line shows something like: 
.Bd -literal
description https://url
.Ed

